The paper discusses monitoring decentralized systems, which involves distributed computing and coordination. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses automata and specifications, which are topics in cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.PL (Programming Languages). The paper also discusses monitoring and verifying system behavior, which is a topic in cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
